%N A188639 Decimal expansion of length/width of a 2nd electrum rectangle.
%C A188639 See A188619 for the definition of 2nd electrum rectangle.  Briefly, it is a rectangle such that the removal of a silver rectangle from one end leaves a golden rectangle.
